    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        "The best thing about my course is that its easy to understand, and the placement is also quite good.",
        "It was good as we went on a visit to 3 substations, where we got to know how electricity is generated and distributed. No, we didnt get any stipend for doing the internship.",
        "This college gives the best placement opportunities with companies like TCS, Infosys, Persistent, Cognizant, Indian Army, etc. The branches of CSE, Biotech, and C-Tech have a good placement record with one of the highest packages per annum.",
        "I dont know much about this, but Ive heard that scholarships are given to students and loans are also provided.",
        "Doubt about campus life, its simply awesome. The gender ratio was 50-50 and the college has indoor and outdoor sports facilities.",
        "They provide breakfast every morning and evening after college. Lunch and dinner are also good there.",
        "Quite good and well-experienced staff, whether its management or lecturers. This whole campus has a huge reputation in the Indian education system. If you choose PCE or PIET, they are the topmost colleges in Nagpur University."
